node.text: A fitness Accountability partner is someone who will help keep you motivated and on track to reach your fitness goals.  After our WMN retreat @mrrushlife and I promised our group that we weren’t gonna stop after the retreat was over.  We will keep this thing going and motivate each other to make this more of a lifestyle.   That’s what the WNM movement is all about.   Fighting obesity and changing lives in our community.    Start a healthier lifestyle today.    Get with a friend and help each other reach your health and fitness goals.  You can start off by joining us on our next WNM retreat next month.    Only a few slots left sign up today!  Weightnomore.info

node.text:
I literally love @mielleorganics! I've seen growth using The Rosemary Mint Scalp and Hair strengthening oil since, you know, I just randomly decided I would chop off ALL my hair one day!

I wanted something new, I wanted to feel sexy, I just had my baby Reign, and being a new mom, you go through a lot with body image. I literally went to the salon for another hairstyle and came out with a new cut! 

My hair has grown back so healthy since then, but it's essential to not be afraid of change for your sanity! Many people would have called me crazy, but having the freedom to just do something drastic made ME feel good, and I was looking good too!!! 

It's been so fun #UNMASKING with my girls @letoyaluckett and @exquisitemo! We went back to our roots and shared our hair stories! It's been a journey, and I'm glad I got to share mine! 

If any new moms are reading this, remember before you're a mom, you're a woman! Take care of yourself so you can take care of others! I do not regret cutting my hair like that, it was freeing, and I legit came upon the hair tip! 

How did you like the #UNMASKED series with #Mielleorganics?

Ok ladies!  Around this time last year I hosted my @weightnomoreinfo #prettygirlsjump double dutch competition. The 1st ladies I want to challenge are @yandysmith @tracisteele @rasheeda #letsgo #prettygirlsjump

🎥 @eyeof_aries 

Jump ropes available at weightnomore.info

node.text: Finally got my Oats & Honey Collection and as you can see me and @reign_beaux is so excited to try it. Thank sis @exquisitemo for sending this over! If you looking to try @mielleorganics new collection Oats N Honey I heard a little birdie say the collection would be back in stock this month 😜 but you heard this from me but you aint hear it from me lol. P.S this collection was designed to help relieve dry itchy scalp, dandruff, and inflammation and is great for ALL hair types! This is their most gentle collection and is targeted towards consumers with a sensitive scalp, although anyone can use it, men and women, alike. #mielle #mielleorganics #mipartnership #mielleoatsandhoney #mtas

node.text: A fitness Accountability partner is someone who will help keep you motivated and on track to reach your fitness goals.  After our WMN retreat @mrrushlife and I promised our group that we weren’t gonna stop after the retreat was over.  We will keep this thing going and motivate each other to make this more of a lifestyle.   That’s what the WNM movement is all about.   Fighting obesity and changing lives in our community.    Start a healthier lifestyle today.    Get with a friend and help each other reach your health and fitness goals.  You can start off by joining us on our next WNM retreat next month.    Only a few slots left sign up today!  Weightnomore.info
